{"h224d0837gd4beg46f3g918dg69be5bbb76fc": ["You! Not another step, hear me?", "fa1a1fbd-2152-40e4-b53d-29e95d54279e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "bc8dbd1a-d47b-af0a-7209-6dd5b48a67c3"], "hbd11ddccgff91g44dfgbcc8g81274cd47054": ["Boss! Got company up here.", "fa1a1fbd-2152-40e4-b53d-29e95d54279e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "ee8e0dbb-a252-895e-65b4-bc2773e0b419"], "h3b557fb3g2b67g4464g8374g221b6b98417d": ["What's this then - trying to creep around us and loot the crypt? Not happening.", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "03c86058-9b67-4538-8d29-0b835b23acce"], "h27aebf4bg042eg4661g8835gfcc653b9fa3c": ["Or is it the ship you're after? Don't matter either way - it's ours<i>, all of it.</i>", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "36326fef-c27a-0e59-c9ff-a28b1d7313c8"], "ha900986eg2dd8g4c53gb623g5e7dddb30335": ["I mean no harm - I'm just looking around.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "8c9b57cd-6fa9-640c-a9d7-b9a742a6e871"], "h8a54c9f1g2886g415eg9176g8d5d9ebf960f": ["First you look, then you touch, then you take!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "19c2bfc2-9d63-e14c-6b7e-da458381299d"], "hc22202e5gc9c6g41eagbe44g883d36327e90": ["The only thing we're sharing with you is our pointy ends - get 'im!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "aaa136f0-cf79-2469-8657-5a6c0e75a673"], "he7042f47g87c0g432dga464gd30a423998e1": ["The only thing we're sharing with you is our pointy ends - get 'er!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "aaa136f0-cf79-2469-8657-5a6c0e75a673"], "ha6565613gce19g459ag9243gcfc398d41772": ["That ship is full of monsters. I wouldn't go near it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "24b707d7-8609-dc59-111e-0bf10028e93a"], "h8dad7a75gce29g4544gae4agccaa89fd45cf": ["Well, uh, in that case...", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "2b3bb056-b972-0ce0-4ec5-36d7ed41f99c"], "h69a80bccg7300g4c22gb5a6g540fa6fa5560": ["C'mon you lot, no point in gettin' killed. Second worm gets the cheese, an' all...", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "be0def25-ea3b-f30d-d216-19a934d3dbdd"], "he27c9206g74d5g405bg8f99g01295a28f108": ["Uh, second <i>mouse </i>gets the cheese, no?", "b5c913f9-f081-45bd-8e95-e34d0735b645", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "ffa72444-03d8-b81e-f97c-3e22b103075a"], "h6a47973dgc557g4f76g9509ga740c578378c": ["Nobody's getting any damn cheese! Now move it!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "fbb8194f-21de-cb62-d725-d6505cb351f6"], "h82665ce1ga6aag44adga58fgcea041a492bc": ["You're all hot air - think you can get us to leave that bounty to you? Not a chance!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "5b853452-771f-6229-1b4b-5ec25bf0ee4d"], "hee06bc23g689bg4330g9de4g44c1796ea1ad": ["What're you lot waiting for? <i>Get 'im!</i>", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "e5562c0c-87a3-5ea1-95a2-d8351969c3f6"], "h14c2418eg46eeg458eg8aaagb42d208121ce": ["What're you lot waiting for? <i>Get 'er!</i>", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "e5562c0c-87a3-5ea1-95a2-d8351969c3f6"], "h89f0988ag3592g4d46gbd54g538868e8b10d": ["I think that ship's an invasion force. Run while you can!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "119a1af9-c269-f4f0-ee99-95abb82ec198"], "h55c56a87g7e18g46d9g8aabgdc1e6c42afa0": ["The only thing you own is your life. Leave before I take that too.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "339ec42a-15c0-c0df-c94a-02df697d47ef"], "h39d18368g7d2eg49b4ga457gb185dc674054": ["<i>Just grin, baring your fangs.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "6da9a1fa-36ee-68d1-d879-7588c5dfe324"], "h1bf6f1dagff45g4bc0gb07eg4ca1012d4899": ["That is my kin's prize, not yours.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "811b156b-5e33-10c4-f4bc-5159a97971fd"], "h89aa2560g1c7eg4d33g8dedg15a024ccd4d9": ["Oh yeah? Well, I don't see any of your kin here to claim it!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "d7349125-c3fc-c421-fe6b-744cbe72da47"], "haae2e849ga5a6g43a7gb411gccf51232fd59": ["What's wrong with his face? Freak.", "b5c913f9-f081-45bd-8e95-e34d0735b645", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "f4c95b2d-8031-2b60-7783-e6c3e329fb8a"], "h4a06d506g6703g40a2gb43ag712844967de8": ["What's wrong with her face? Freak.", "b5c913f9-f081-45bd-8e95-e34d0735b645", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "f4c95b2d-8031-2b60-7783-e6c3e329fb8a"], "ha051e1dbg55d8g4400g8f26g643f08330b01": ["<i>Dead</i> freak. Get 'im!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "db84bd29-44bc-c0f6-28b5-68720d6f6b96"], "h9865914dge174g4e9cg94d4gc2891706d566": ["<i>Dead</i> freak. Get 'er!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "db84bd29-44bc-c0f6-28b5-68720d6f6b96"], "h93dea017gaa34g419eg97fdgd75267ba44ec": ["Nothing's yours but your life - and I can take that from you just as easily.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "baec6f91-b1c3-6598-6fa9-23c998ac2d08"], "h9105f870g89a4g42ceg9310ga7224fcae2bf": ["Oh yeah? Well we're... we're -", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "74cb6d94-7363-7044-a6f1-1ee02a168a77"], "h5ae9176egf8a0g4a00gb1d4g2b13d152a8fb": ["I ain't fighting him. Not a chance.", "b5c913f9-f081-45bd-8e95-e34d0735b645", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "829d87da-2fef-5a80-4395-9b46efc92c5a"], "hdc894218g63d9g4f38g850dgf9ff0f03c64b": ["I ain't fighting her. Not a chance.", "b5c913f9-f081-45bd-8e95-e34d0735b645", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "829d87da-2fef-5a80-4395-9b46efc92c5a"], "h962df7b1g6d40g492fg82a4g281d2d1507bc": ["... we're, uh... we're leaving! C'mon, move it!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "561af675-770e-4632-5d63-e08bcacdf69d"], "h4ee4933eg970cg4a56g86afg2c2745900ff4": ["Take your best shot - you'll only get one.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "62271f98-279d-34e7-dbd5-8e6ddba953ab"], "h6cdc39a8gf6d7g463bga39eg699124695913": ["That ship's full of poisonous vapours. Probably demonic. I'd stay away.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "1a7a6f02-b2e6-1a6e-3e6e-0c1fd0dd447d"], "h29d1668fg4118g4d8cgbe12g34269084ab9e": ["Poisonous wha...?", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "cddd046a-c1cd-6d55-ce26-5e76cabc4f8e"], "h8e0d3a9cg65bfg4bedg8a72g72d7f4f90774": ["Don't like the sound of this, boss...", "b5c913f9-f081-45bd-8e95-e34d0735b645", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "8915344d-ec91-607a-aa26-12f1bb902ad1"], "h92938499gaf60g44a3ga2d2g2842bd2e426c": ["<i>Attack.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditWestInteraction.html", "f53d3116-b5cb-5db4-2464-24af2e61526a"]}